Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.10,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.13,0:00:05.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年的名字是橘纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.22,0:00:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,17岁的高中二年生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.22,0:00:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在两年前的圣诞节受到失恋的打击
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.91,0:00:17.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那旧伤而对恋爱感到畏惧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.30,0:00:18.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽如此
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.99,0:00:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前他就不是主动争取恋爱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.34,0:00:23.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其说软弱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:25.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不如说以失恋为借口…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.70,0:00:26.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.57,0:00:28.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能到此为止吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.37,0:00:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 此少年为本作的主人公
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.04,0:00:41.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可爱的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.95,0:00:45.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸部很…很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.90,0:00:48.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年跟少女命运的邂逅…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.84,0:00:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还未能实现
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.12,0:02:24.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假后的第二学期
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.12,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.13,0:02:30.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经过夏季的诸多活动 校内诞生了大量情侣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.41,0:02:33.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 今天要在食堂把夏季限定发售
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.37,0:02:36.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能补充体力的四川凉面吃个够
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.50,0:02:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,补充多余的体力要干啥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.90,0:02:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.38,0:02:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就得为关键时候时刻准备
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.49,0:02:45.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大将 一起如何
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.54,0:02:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 我不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.44,0:02:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的夏天 很遗憾的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.58,0:02:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连那种活动也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.92,0:02:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘同学 梅原同学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.21,0:02:58.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假布置的物理作业
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.90,0:03:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放学时要收齐所以请按时交上来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.36,0:03:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.95,0:03:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.45,0:03:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 不是影印给你了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.28,0:03:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 说起来也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.96,0:03:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘记了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.33,0:03:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石垣老师很可怕的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.93,0:03:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…哦 是放学后交吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.32,0:03:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就在第五节课
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.01,0:03:19.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶作业是不对的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.04,0:03:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午休报销了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.82,0:03:22.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不吃午饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.22,0:03:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法 我帮你买些回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.69,0:03:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 我的挚友 大恩没齿难忘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.92,0:03:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 麻烦帮我买猪扒三文治和肉饼三文治
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.80,0:03:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有四川凉面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.99,0:03:35.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.07,0:03:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.81,0:03:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.31,0:03:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真焦急啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.03,0:03:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.86,0:03:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在转弯处要小心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.14,0:03:54.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.56,0:03:59.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 森岛学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.20,0:04:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女看着钱包 心中暗自觉得可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.65,0:04:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 请问
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.26,0:04:12.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.31,0:04:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 梨穗子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.55,0:00:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.89,0:04:18.19,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(300,450)\fad(150,150)}中多纱江编
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.89,0:04:18.19,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(300,500)\fad(150,150)}第一章
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.89,0:04:18.19,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(300,540)\fad(150,150)}学妹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.55,0:00:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.07,0:04:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我暑假旅行时候给纯一买了手信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.05,0:04:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 钱包
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.17,0:04:20.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅行？你跟家人一起去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.52,0:04:22.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 很好玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.96,0:04:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手信下次再给你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.74,0:04:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.65,0:04:28.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.85,0:04:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问 请问
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.36,0:04:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候 少女的声音不可能传到少年耳中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.32,0:04:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为 少年脑中浮现了挚友焦急等待的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.40,0:04:47.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要尽快买到面包 回到他身边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.74,0:04:49.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奔跑吧 快奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.28,0:04:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅原怀着信赖等待着你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.29,0:04:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让一让
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.86,0:04:59.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.32,0:05:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.74,0:05:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 猪扒三文治和肉饼面包还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.82,0:05:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四川凉面卖完了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.77,0:05:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 梅原
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.79,0:05:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 就买这个给梅原
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.42,0:05:25.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要迅速点所以就吃乌龙面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.82,0:05:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很费时
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.84,0:05:31.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也吃面包吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.94,0:05:37.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧 钱包
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.48,0:05:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人的吧 诶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.70,0:05:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪 刚才还在的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.35,0:05:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.97,0:05:50.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那是我的钱包
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.60,0:05:54.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是你帮我捡回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.88,0:05:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在 在楼梯那里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.74,0:05:59.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.34,0:06:02.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才在楼梯撞到的时候掉下的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.51,0:06:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮了大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.27,0:06:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有这个鳕鱼子钱包 午饭就吃不成了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.18,0:06:10.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 鳕鱼子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:12.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳕鱼子…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.92,0:06:15.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧 这孩子 是之前的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.31,0:06:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 你之前是穿着其他学校的校服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.76,0:06:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是转校生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.24,0:06:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一年级学生？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.02,0:06:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪个班的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.79,0:06:29.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你叫什么名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.96,0:06:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.81,0:06:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告 告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.45,0:06:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.25,0:06:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.35,0:06:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.72,0:06:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在我校激烈的午餐争夺战中败阵了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.63,0:06:54.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微晚一点出去就这样子了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.49,0:06:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要跟你分了这个小面包吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.90,0:07:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了大将
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.54,0:07:02.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是要找到她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.10,0:07:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.80,0:07:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好好道谢的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.52,0:07:07.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我可以整个吃掉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.04,0:07:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.50,0:07:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 美也
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.28,0:07:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年级学生有像这样把头发扎在两边的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.56,0:07:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的…难道说是双马尾吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.87,0:07:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.79,0:07:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外还有点胆怯 像小动物一样可爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.04,0:07:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛水灵灵的 个子不高…还有该怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.17,0:07:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是“该大的地方都大”吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.10,0:07:37.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.71,0:07:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我可能知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.72,0:07:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过那个人怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.01,0:07:46.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才她帮我捡回了这个鳕鱼子钱包
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.08,0:07:48.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想好好道谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.83,0:07:50.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.88,0:07:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.78,0:07:54.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 纱江 欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.45,0:07:58.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样 在饭堂买到午餐了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.24,0:08:02.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.42,0:08:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来作介绍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.55,0:08:07.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是中多纱江
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.94,0:08:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后这有点色色的是美也的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.43,0:08:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美 美也 你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.51,0:08:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 刚才还色迷迷地说“该大的地方都大”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.45,0:08:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.60,0:08:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真羞耻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.85,0:08:24.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我也了解哥哥的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.55,0:08:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.28,0:08:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱江身材很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.79,0:08:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美也经常很羡慕地叫她让我摸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.56,0:08:33.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让 让你摸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.68,0:08:38.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害 软绵绵的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.27,0:08:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好柔软啊 不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.07,0:08:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 表情很色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.72,0:08:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.34,0:08:53.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱江 我哥就是这样子 你们好好相处
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.99,0:08:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才也说过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.95,0:09:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你之前还穿着其他学校的校服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.28,0:09:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱江是第二学期初刚转校过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.19,0:09:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也终于拿到校服了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.88,0:09:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才帮我捡到钱包 真的很感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.80,0:09:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为突然跑起来 要找很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.49,0:09:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为纱江人很好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.63,0:09:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.98,0:09:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钱包…很可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.42,0:09:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.35,0:09:27.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能好好道谢就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.80,0:09:33.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一次 少年少女真正地邂逅了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.32,0:09:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后数日
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.03,0:09:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.87,0:09:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.75,0:09:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘 橘学长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.13,0:09:48.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.04,0:09:50.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狗…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.51,0:09:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.60,0:09:54.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可怕了 我走不过去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.06,0:09:55.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.73,0:09:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那户人家 门的另一边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.79,0:10:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一只没被绑着的狗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.65,0:10:01.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.49,0:10:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想会不会到这边来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.93,0:10:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有扇门在应该没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.59,0:10:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我跟你一起走过去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.43,0:10:15.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.33,0:10:17.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想两个人应该没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.18,0:10:21.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 非常…感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.95,0:10:24.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都不可怕…应该
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.94,0:10:27.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.41,0:10:28.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.57,0:10:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.66,0:10:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 原来是小狗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.37,0:10:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 没事的 不用怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.86,0:11:00.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.58,0:11:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中多 中多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.49,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.54,0:11:13.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.60,0:11:16.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.63,0:11:18.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.32,0:11:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正已经通过了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.52,0:11:23.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你连小狗都怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.16,0:11:25.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.91,0:11:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了 决定要点什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.44,0:11:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰 你表情是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.76,0:11:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵 难道这位是你女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.56,0:11:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.04,0:11:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真见外 不用隐藏了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.17,0:11:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都说不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.73,0:11:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我介绍一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.72,0:11:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是美也的同班同学中多纱江
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.55,0:11:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是我的女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.99,0:11:56.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫棚钉薰 是纯一的同学 多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.91,0:11:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟薰中学的时候就认识了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.00,0:12:01.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了 到一边去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.70,0:12:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我还没听你说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.85,0:12:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.80,0:12:05.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.62,0:12:07.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.06,0:12:08.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.47,0:12:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没说要点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.95,0:12:13.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那回事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.36,0:12:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我要咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.59,0:12:19.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给囊中羞涩的客人自由咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.55,0:12:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.15,0:12:21.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.23,0:12:24.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.10,0:12:27.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 两杯咖啡对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.01,0:12:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.02,0:12:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵 那么不打扰你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.03,0:12:35.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.61,0:12:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看得很入迷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.24,0:12:43.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得制服…很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.54,0:12:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.67,0:12:47.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对那些感兴趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.54,0:12:49.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 一直想试穿一次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.50,0:12:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中多没有做兼职吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.99,0:12:56.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 因为之前的学校不允许
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.14,0:12:59.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  我也没做过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.82,0:13:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们学校允许做兼职的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.89,0:13:03.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做一下也无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.15,0:13:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.08,0:13:06.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 要不问一下薰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.52,0:13:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问问这里有没有招人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.63,0:13:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.06,0:13:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了 你们的咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.10,0:13:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要这些吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.88,0:13:23.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖啡可以自由添 要的话请随便
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.85,0:13:26.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 请慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.82,0:13:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下 薰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.21,0:13:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这间店现在还招兼职工吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.68,0:13:34.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 一直在招人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.95,0:13:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.75,0:13:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想做兼职吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.95,0:13:40.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.00,0:13:43.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能告诉我们兼职招聘的详情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.03,0:13:46.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊 还有一小时左右就下班了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.19,0:13:47.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后再跟你们说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.21,0:13:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.89,0:13:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那待会见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.96,0:13:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.04,0:14:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然想做兼职 但是……
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.48,0:14:04.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先听一下细节吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.96,0:14:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰一定能帮到你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.47,0:14:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她虽然笨 但很可靠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.60,0:14:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.85,0:14:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 今天突然有人请假
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.02,0:14:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要替班
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.97,0:14:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.91,0:14:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谈不成真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.95,0:14:26.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 没事 不要介意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.83,0:14:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实呢 这里做兼职要通过一个简单的考试
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.69,0:14:34.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一般的面试
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.63,0:14:35.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简单来说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.39,0:14:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是确认你能否跟客人沟通和给客人送菜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.80,0:14:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会很难
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.21,0:14:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.51,0:14:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.43,0:14:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送菜应该没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.98,0:14:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟客人沟通就……
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.44,0:14:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一起练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.15,0:14:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.88,0:14:59.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.43,0:15:07.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候少女并不知晓 少年根本不知该怎样练习
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.75,0:15:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 于是就到我们家练习了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.61,0:15:15.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥突然带纱江来 真吓我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.71,0:15:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 明白了 交给美也吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.64,0:15:23.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得纱江要挑战兼职
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.41,0:15:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会帮忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.79,0:15:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 美也
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.77,0:15:29.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那美也要怎样做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.01,0:15:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美也就扮演客人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.81,0:15:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那哥哥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.53,0:15:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？我就……
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.18,0:15:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.22,0:15:42.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对了 我是教官
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.06,0:15:44.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我扮演教官的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.43,0:15:44.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.55,0:15:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 叫一下试试
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.37,0:15:48.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教…教官
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.24,0:15:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教官 教官 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.15,0:15:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样决定了 我要严格训练你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.02,0:16:01.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如美也所说 中多很怕生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.82,0:16:03.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.62,0:16:05.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 如果不彻底改正的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.24,0:16:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兼职录取考试就不能通过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.54,0:16:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 也许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.29,0:16:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要特训 努力争取通过测试
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.48,0:16:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 美也会协助你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.04,0:16:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱江 能坚持吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.42,0:16:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.72,0:16:31.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我要努力试试
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.23,0:16:37.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 首先是让客人听到你声音的特训
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.35,0:16:41.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 学长…不 教官
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.51,0:16:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有一个家里经营寿司店的朋友梅原
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.16,0:16:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在店里帮忙的时候他老爸说过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.09,0:16:53.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说“欢迎光临”的时候声音要从肚子里发出来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.85,0:16:57.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从肚子里发出声音吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.10,0:17:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 所以为了发出声音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.91,0:17:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先练习让肚子膨胀收缩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.51,0:17:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.42,0:17:11.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何 行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.45,0:17:13.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 我不是很清楚要怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.97,0:17:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把手放在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.51,0:17:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.70,0:17:26.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.73,0:17:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那试一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.83,0:17:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 啊咧咧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.36,0:17:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.99,0:17:35.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.04,0:17:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特训 特训
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.66,0:17:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.86,0:17:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 吸气让肚子涨起来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.97,0:17:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 呼气让肚子缩回来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.09,0:17:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没涨起来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.94,0:17:51.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 吸气
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.89,0:18:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸气 吸气…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.35,0:18:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 教官
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.98,0:18:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.25,0:18:11.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 老哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.45,0:18:12.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.61,0:18:14.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正常的呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.60,0:18:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不止要吸气 还要呼气
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.63,0:18:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 接下来是送菜的特训
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.59,0:18:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是的 教官
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.42,0:18:28.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 把咖啡送到我这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.82,0:18:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 教官
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.42,0:18:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等…了 啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.43,0:18:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好热 好热…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.35,0:18:43.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.78,0:18:47.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.69,0:18:48.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.61,0:18:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.78,0:18:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥你这变态
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.36,0:18:56.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,映入妹妹眼里的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.65,0:19:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在朋友面前脱下裤子的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.88,0:19:04.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.11,0:19:06.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不 下次再来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.14,0:19:10.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长 非常…感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.47,0:19:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.73,0:19:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 是哥哥不好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.19,0:19:16.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做些被误解的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.25,0:19:17.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.66,0:19:20.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美也 好羡慕你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.32,0:19:21.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.06,0:19:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有学长…不 教…教官这样的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.66,0:19:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.07,0:19:30.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我是独生女
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.10,0:19:35.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的哥哥你要随时可以给你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.46,0:19:35.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.12,0:19:37.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.33,0:19:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久没玩过背人猜拳了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.47,0:19:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 你说真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.18,0:19:42.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背人猜拳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.64,0:19:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 输掉的人要背起赢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.31,0:19:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算是解释吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.39,0:19:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.13,0:19:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出「布（パー）」赢的话就说波罗雪糕（パインアイス）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.36,0:19:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出「剪（グー）」赢了的话就说奶汁烤菜（グラタン）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.36,0:19:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说出多少个字就背着人走几步
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.82,0:19:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.92,0:19:57.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.41,0:20:00.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,规则是败者背着胜者走与字数相应的步数
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.30,0:20:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有说过的不能再说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.89,0:20:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.16,0:20:05.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.05,0:20:07.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩吧 玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.43,0:20:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.86,0:20:10.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就在此大显身手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.21,0:20:12.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还嫩着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.15,0:20:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剪刀石头布
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.77,0:20:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 剪刀石头布
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.14,0:20:19.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 是哥哥输了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.63,0:20:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真弱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.81,0:20:25.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 输掉的哥哥快背起纱江
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.74,0:20:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 我…不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.57,0:20:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.82,0:20:32.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背人猜拳是绝对的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.23,0:20:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.29,0:20:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那就鼓足干劲上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.61,0:20:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.69,0:20:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘻嘻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.32,0:20:44.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有劳了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.92,0:20:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次我不会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.53,0:20:57.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年其实觉得这样永远输下去亦无仿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.71,0:21:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 应该说希望永远输下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.28,0:21:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 重吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.33,0:21:04.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 完全不重
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.95,0:21:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 怎么办gu开头有什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.73,0:21:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丰满的身材
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.32,0:21:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.08,0:21:15.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 从肚子里发出声音 来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.90,0:21:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丰满的身材
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.96,0:21:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再大声点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.38,0:21:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丰满的身材 来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.98,0:21:28.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丰满的身材
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.01,0:21:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经少女口中说出的略带H色彩的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.10,0:21:38.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转变成更加H的话传到少年耳中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.32,0:21:41.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,声音挺响亮的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.13,0:21:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.99,0:21:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丰 满 的 身 材
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.59,0:21:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕阳之下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.17,0:21:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年背起了少女
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.25,0:21:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炎炎夏日即将完结之时
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.21,0:22:03.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人命运的齿轮已经开始转动
